  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Join the cast of iCarly!\nJoin the cast of iCarly! Their latest web show has been deleted at the last minute and you need to help them go live by creating a new show from scratch! You'll recreate your favorite skits from iCarly and even create all-new skits with your very own backdrops, gameplay objects, music, and more. It's a whole new iCarly experience that you can play on your own or with your friends!",
